__data__.text: Breely helps to manage and automate every customer interaction so you can focus on the core of your business. Now you can create lead forms to capture client information, offer class and workshop booking, offer booking 1:1 appointments, and sell memberships.

SpeakclearlyAI is an AI-powered audio enhancement tool designed to help creators, professionals, and businesses achieve crystal-clear, professional-quality audio effortlessly. Whether you're recording podcasts, videos, presentations, or interviews, SpeakclearlyAI removes filler words (like "ums" and "uhs"), eliminates background noise, and enhances pacing—all with the power of advanced artificial intelligence.

Cert0 is a unique platform that lets you prove that you created a file at a specific time by generating a unique digital fingerprint (hash) on your device and storing it on the blockchain. This means no one can change or fake the record, and you get a certificate with a timestamp to show ownership. It’s simple—upload a file, get a proof, and keep it for legal protection or personal assurance. Whether you're a creator, freelancer, or business, Cert0 helps you secure your work without relying on third parties or complicated processes.

Blocksfusion is a digital construction platform combining real-time collaboration, GitHub-style version control, and a seamless bridge between virtual and physical building. Users can create, edit, and share Lego-style projects, explore them in simulation modes, and order real bricks to bring their designs to life. Whether you're a solo builder, a team collaborator, or an educator, Blocksfusion redefines how we build, play, and innovate together.

Amoeba AI is the neuro-symbolic AI powered data scientist for GTM teams. It allows marketing and revenue teams to be able to analyze data at scale, design experiments related to efforts, simulate scenarios - all in the name of getting the most out of their data and efforts. The underlying architecture goes beyond LLMs to give you the why and the how instead of just the what.

Paperplane is your perfect starter-kit to build your next big thing in days, not weeks. Simple, yet powerful, clear and concise, utilizing powerful tools and libraries to not just get you started, but to get you started right.

RenderCut is a SaaS tool designed for video editors and content creators. With just a few clicks, you can add stylish, professional subtitles to your videos, making them more engaging, accessible, and ready to reach a wider audience. Whether you're a beginner or a seasoned creator, RenderCut saves time, boosts engagement, and ensures your videos stand out.

Searchlens is a powerful keyword discovery and topic research software designed to help businesses, content creators, and marketers stay ahead in the competitive digital landscape. With just a single seed phrase, it generates thousands of highly targeted, long-tail niche keywords in seconds. It provides comprehensive and profound SEO data, rather than generic SEO data provided by Ubersuggest, Ahrefs and others.

OneOver is a platform that brings the best AI tools together in one place. Access top models for text and image generation, compare results, and stay on top of the latest breakthroughs—all with one subscription. It’s simple, customizable, and designed to make working with AI easy and efficient.

Boxsy is on a mission to empower startups and the entire ecosystem by providing a seamless operational hub designed to make entrepreneurship more successful. Our vision is to simplify the operational complexities that often hinder growth, offering founders and their partners the tools, insights, and connectivity they need to thrive. From streamlined reporting to expert-backed solutions, Boxsy is here to help startups scale smarter and build stronger, more impactful businesses.

QubeGuard is an innovative security solution designed specifically to protect API endpoints from a spectrum of cyber threats. It effectively shields APIs by detecting and blocking malicious activities in real time, ensuring the integrity and confidentiality of data transmissions. With its advanced security features, QubeGuard provides businesses with critical tools to monitor, analyze, and respond to threats, thereby maintaining a secure digital environment. Easy to integrate and manage, it supports a proactive approach to cybersecurity, helping organizations safeguard their API infrastructure against emerging and sophisticated attacks.

Zparse is an AI-powered, no-code platform helping business users transform, integrate, and monitor data without technical skills. It solves challenges like: - Manually transferring data (e.g., copy-pasting XLSX, CSV, etc.), - Waiting on engineers for system connections, - Manually onboarding customer data, - Linking systems with external apps via costly custom connectors. Unlike most competitors in the ETL/Reverse ETL space, Zparse is built for non-technical teams. It's intuitive design and AI simplify mapping, integrating, and monitoring data from any source to any destination in just a few clicks. With Zparse, teams save hours, rely less on engineers, and streamline workflows.

Apparatus.ai is an AI-powered platform designed to revolutionize business forecasting, marketing, and operations. It offers intuitive tools for revenue forecasting, scenario planning, and campaign optimization, enabling businesses to make smarter, data-driven decisions. With Apparatus.ai, users can easily model business outcomes, adapt strategies in real-time, and collaborate effectively to drive growth.

ValidateAIdea is a SaaS platform designed to help founders and entrepreneurs assess the viability of their business ideas. By leveraging advanced AI , ValidateAIdea generates comprehensive reports that evaluate key aspects such as market demand, competition, and business model etc. It also find leads for your idea to connect to potential customer. You also get 1 credit free on signup.

Gistr is a powerful knowledge management platform designed to help users organize, annotate, and share information effortlessly. It combines the simplicity of bookmarking and note-taking with advanced AI features for summarization, insights, and enhanced productivity. Users can create curated playlists of their notes and bookmarks, tag content for easy categorization, and share ideas on a social feed or keep them private. Ideal for professionals, students, and teams, Gistr transforms how you manage knowledge, making it accessible, collaborative, and personalized across devices.

Stevie AI is an SEO tool that helps startups and small businesses get much-needed organic traffic from Google using the same methods SEO Agencies use (costing $1500+/month). The methods are simple: We automated the workflows agencies use to get the best result for SEO and turned them into simple, one-click, tasks that can take you from a URL to optimal keywords to generating blogs and landing page texts - the whole process tasks less than 3 minutes (check out the video for a demo!)

TechBlitz is an open-source, mobile-friendly web development platform that empowers aspiring developers through short-form, real-world coding content to ensure they become better developer. AI-powered coding roadmaps, on-demand question help and coding report creation ensures developers get a unique, personalized expierence.

Retellio is an AI briefing tool for leaders who can't listen to every call. Retellio makes it easy for B2B founders and leaders to stay connected to customers by distilling hours of feedback into critical insights—unfiltered, curated, and delivered via private RSS feed to your fav podcast app so you can listen anywhere and anytime. It's a powerful way to hear what matters most without losing context or the customer’s voice.

Uplyt.io is a data analytics tool designed for marketers, consultants, and small-to-medium businesses struggling to extract actionable insights from Google Analytics 4 and Google Ads. Often, key data points that could drive business growth go unnoticed or are too complex to interpret. Uplyt bridges this gap by making analytics simple, accessible, and actionable.

It automatically transcribes your meetings, generates concise summaries, and highlights actionable insights so you can focus on what truly matters. Whether you’re a solo entrepreneur or part of a growing team, Recap simplifies the way you manage meeting notes, track important decisions, and share key outcomes—effortlessly.

GeniusGate is a DIY copywriting tool designed to function like a professional copywriter. It asks specific questions about your business, gathers your inputs, and generates personalized, tailored copy to meet your needs.

Aiverse Design is the largest library of AI-UX interactions, curated from top companies designing for AI. IndieLaunch is a Next.js landing page template designed for indie hackers and startup founders to quickly create a professional web presence. It aims to help entrepreneurs bypass technical complexities and focus on validating their product ideas. The template offers a quick setup with Tailwind CSS and pre-designed components, allowing users to launch a landing page in minutes. The template provides a basic structure for showcasing a product or idea.

IndieVoice is a platform, where indie hackers give and get detailed feedbacks on their SaaS projects. It solves the struggle to obtain quality feedback from like-minded people. At IndieVoice giving feedback becomes a currency, which lets you getting quality feedbacks on your own project. This is a community where everone gets better off at the end! Our supervised favor-based system guarantees detailed insights from all aspects of your project including: idea, UI, UX, core features, performance etc. At IndieVoice there are no inequalities triggered by popularity, past achievements, X audience. Only the quality of your work matters!

Blok is a practical solution for reducing phone distractions by introducing a physical barrier to app access. To unlock apps, you must physically tap the device, creating an extra step that helps prevent impulsive usage. The Blok app lets you manage which apps are blocked and customize your settings. By separating Blok from your usual phone use area, you ensure that distractions are kept at bay. This physical approach promotes a more focused and productive environment. Blok is ideal for improving your screen time habits and staying on task. Embrace a new way to manage distractions with Blok’s innovative design.
